sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant X as Exchange
    participant Q as Queue
    participant W as Matcher
    participant St as Strategy
    participant B as OrderBook
    participant Pub as Publisher
    participant L as Listeners

    Client->>X: placeOrder order
    X->>Q: enqueue PlaceOrderCommand with future
    Note over X,Q: producer returns, then client blocks on the future

    Note over W,B: matcher thread is the only thread touching the book
    W->>Q: dequeue command
    W->>St: match book and order
    St->>B: read best opposite level
    St->>B: fill resting orders FIFO then remove filled
    St->>B: rest remainder for LIMIT only
    St-->>W: trades

    W->>Pub: publish trades off thread
    Pub-->>L: onTrade async never blocks matching
    W->>X: complete the future with trades
    X-->>Client: return trades as join unblocks
